title: HackMIT 2025
description: Join us for the biggest hackathon of the year! Build innovative projects, network with peers, and win amazing prizes. 48-hour coding marathon with workshops and mentorship.

title: AI/ML Workshop: Introduction to Deep Learning
description: Learn the fundamentals of deep learning and neural networks. Hands-on session with TensorFlow and PyTorch. Perfect for beginners!

title: Web Development Bootcamp
description: Intensive 3-day bootcamp covering React, Node.js, and modern web development practices. Build a full-stack application from scratch.

title: Mobile App Competition
description: Build the best mobile app and compete for $10,000 in prizes. Teams welcome! Focus on iOS and Android development.

title: Cloud Infrastructure Seminar
description: Learn about cloud computing, containerization, and modern DevOps practices. Hands-on AWS and Docker workshops.

title: Data Science Hackathon
description: Solve real-world data problems using machine learning and analytics. Great for beginners! Work with real datasets.

title: React Native Workshop
description: Build cross-platform mobile apps with React Native. Learn from experts and build your first app in one day!

title: Blockchain Development Course
description: Learn Solidity and build smart contracts on Ethereum. Create your own DeFi application.

title: IoT Hackathon
description: Build innovative IoT solutions using Raspberry Pi and sensors. Create smart home automation projects.

title: Full Stack Development Summit
description: A comprehensive summit covering frontend, backend, and DevOps. Network with industry professionals.

title: Computer Vision Workshop
description: Introduction to computer vision with OpenCV and TensorFlow. Build image recognition models.

title: DevOps & Microservices Conference
description: Learn about microservices architecture, containerization, and CI/CD pipelines.
